nifold $L\\equiv {\\rm graph}(Du)$ is the phase function\n$\\theta$ of the tangent spaces of $L$. On $L$ it satisfies the equation $\\nabla\n\\psi = -JH$ where $H$ is the mean curvature vector field of $L$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 14:29:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2020 19:45:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 15 Mar 2020 13:57:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 14:38:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-23"}
