ose that the disruption of near-Sun\nasteroids as well as the anomalous brightening and destruction processes that\naffect SOHO comets occur through meteoroid erosion, that is, the removal of\nmaterial through impacts by high-speed near-Sun meteoroids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 15:03:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
